      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771860167530,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirements\n\n1. User can see the location of the driver in real time (should it be real time, or can we have some delay 10s)\n2. User will have a ETA of the order\n3. Dasher can see a route in real time for the order",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Functional Requirements\n\n1. User can see the location of the driver in real time (should it be real time, or can we have some delay 10s)\n2. User will have a ETA of the order\n3. Dasher can see a route in real time for the order",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tcoVJcMxqmJmhzC-DPePM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 78.5510508559876,
      "y": 263.1896704995081,
      "width": 222.19180297851562,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
