      "locked": false,
      "text": "Non-Functional Requirements",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Non-Functional Requirements",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "CMvlaQ67j3EkDnlQ18q3E",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 84.3489531517601,
      "y": 299.29692119873704,
      "width": 513.45556640625,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a2",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 250937661,
      "version": 57,
      "versionNonce": 2031937693,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771860420045,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. Availability over consistency — a few seconds of delay in\nlocation updates is acceptable",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1. Availability over consistency — a few seconds of delay in location updates is acceptable",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hJYQrqQ5XN_w8UPS_l_vA",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 81.47598799114684,
      "y": 348.1407121669637,
      "width": 560.2554321289062,
      "height": 20,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a3",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1204059411,
      "version": 80,
      "versionNonce": 36141107,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771860425140,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2. Low latency — updates should feel near real-time (~5-10s delay max)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "2. Low latency — updates should feel near real-time (~5-10s delay max)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "F8YMoK0XnoFwX-PvHoa6o",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 81.85286566360685,
      "y": 384.58953800007424,
      "width": 534.8314819335938,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1654378909,
      "version": 93,
      "versionNonce": 1673307133,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771860428859,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3. High scalability — 50M daily users, 50% ordering, peaks at lunch\nand dinner",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3. High scalability — 50M daily users, 50% ordering, peaks at lunch and dinner",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "GNdayD0Uir-lQQzVQ4JYZ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 79.53490642130686,
      "y": 443.26658946923123,
      "width": 483.1035461425781,
      "height": 40,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 49898163,
      "version": 83,
      "versionNonce": 800575987,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1771860434315,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4. Fault tolerant — dasher connectivity drops should be\nhandled gracefully",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4. Fault tolerant — dasher connectivity drops should be handled gracefully",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
